{"tid":1793043,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如 何 引 爆 二 零 二 零 政 治 工 潮 ？","createTime":"2019-12-22T05:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T11:47:21.000Z","uid":147664,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f38dded81f598562ac9ecd43a7e5ee39e4c544a9","tid":1793043,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"黎明行動前開左一個post講被罷工<br />\n如 何 製 造 大 規 模 被 罷 工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700451</a><br />\n1001後有絲打幫手開多左個<br />\n<br />\n如果你而家入去睇返 <br />\n就會見到好多本身大家都覺得無可能既事<br />\n都發生左<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大量教師無法回校 <br />\n有牙力的中學校長會出記招<br />\n教育局宣布停課 林鄭跌入圈套<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各行各業無法運作 <br />\n社會停擺將近兩星期</span><br />\n </span><br />\n<br />\n但係 呢啲短暫既甜頭 <br />\n全部都係手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用鮮血 用汗水 用前途</span></span> <br />\n犧牲所得<br />\n而我好認同黎明行動條Formula<br />\n已經切切實實俾狗破解左<br />\n再做落去只會削弱我地既氣勢 犧牲更多手足<br />\n而教育局係呢一星期所進行既清算行動<br />\n已經話俾教育界人士聽 你地退無可退 <br />\n<br />\n你可能會懊惱 而家咁既情況有咩可以做到<br />\n我可以話俾你聽 而家首要做既事情係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一股團結教師既新力量！</span></span><br />\n人民話事 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可 既主導權係我地手上！<br />\n<br />\n而從巴絲既留言所見<br />\n都幾肯定<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上連登有ac既教師為數眾多</span></span><br />\n請你地認清事實 <br />\n相信自己係呢場運動既力量有幾咁舉足輕重<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老師既參與係歷史多數既革命<br />\n都擔當住重要既角色</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然你呢一刻可能覺得自己有道德枷鎖<br />\n罷唔到工 唔緊要<br />\n大家所承擔 所背負既包袱都唔一樣<br />\n無人有資格批評別人罷唔罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係請你唔好將2019年香港發生既事情就此忘記<br />\n花少少時間 凝聚自己行業既力量</span><br />\n<br />\n老師們請Follow Like Subscribe<br />\n教育界新工會籌備組 教育同行<br />\n<br />\nInstagram <a href=\"https://bit.ly/358b191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F358b191&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=9aa45dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/358b191</a><br />\n@standbyeducatorshk<br />\n<br />\nFacebook <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/教育同行工會籌備組-101323324668085/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%90%8C%E8%A1%8C%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E7%B1%8C%E5%82%99%E7%B5%84-101323324668085%2F&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=5006574f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/教育同行工會籌備組-101323324668085/</a><br />\n<br />\nTG Channel <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=c0d50fe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 <br />\n教育同行TG channel發放最新消息<br />\n需要教師幫手填同Spread一份有關<br />\n教師專業自主既調查 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBOQHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBOQHA.jpg&h=20f3c61e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請前往 <a href=\"https://forms.gle/wsjamBydEshoNPqs7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FwsjamBydEshoNPqs7&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=31139d76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/wsjamBydEshoNPqs7</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">加入工會 團結力量 做好分工<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個有行動力有號召力既工會 <br />\n首要條件係要 夠 多 人！！！</span></span><br />\n其他工會資料請前往二百萬三罷聯合陣線 <br />\nTG channel&nbsp; <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=af199a83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a></div>"},{"pid":"423d512060e1d9ca9d16a244e4aa7338184daac6","tid":1793043,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"自推 十連  1/10<br />\n老師們 阻你少少時間 填份問卷<br />\n